AAMCCS係一個令人跳出框框既地方，例如透過探討性別同身份課題，我地可以重新思考生活中看似非黑即白既事。AAMCCSers, play hard, work harder!






Tina Yung

2014-2016 Associate of Arts in Media, Cultural and Creative Studies - Media and Cultural Studies Theme
