My gain in SPACE is beyond expectation because the new challenges I encountered here had forced me to grow up. There are always paths to our destinations and though it may not be the way people agree with, it sure will be the best if we are determined about it.






Wong Yi Hang

2016 文學副學士（媒體、文化及創意）　二年級學生
